The FlashDevelop plugin for Spaceport has all the functionality to build and test games using the Spaceport platform.

Steps to test the updater process
* Add the merged Installer to the update package EX: 0.0.3.0.zip
* Upload the ZIP to the update directory
* Delete the plugins form the FlashDevelop/Plugins folder
 - InstallerCore.dll
 - SpaceportPlugin.dll
 - SpaceportUpdaterPlugin.dll
 - PluginCommon.dll
* Delete the Spaceport folder from  FlashDevelop/Data
* Run the installer in GUI mode with the latest update package
* Once installed successfully, run through the update process completely
